padding: 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;El producto debe tener un SKU asignado.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr style=&quot;height:50.646484375pt&quot;&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-width: 1.125pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Descripción&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-width: 1.125pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;El sistema solicita el nombre y la descripción del producto. El usuario ingresa la información [Excepción 1][Excepción 2]. El sistema valida los datos y registra la información descriptiva del producto, confirmando la operación.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr style=&quot;height:60.75pt&quot;&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-width: 1.125pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Excepciones&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-width: 1.125pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;502&quot; data-end=&quot;637&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 11px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span data-start=&quot;502&quot; data-end=&quot;518&quot;&gt;Excepción 1:&lt;/span&gt; El nombre contiene menos de 3 o más de 100 caracteres. El sistema informa el error y solicita corregir la información.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;639&quot; data-end=&quot;765&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 11px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span data-start=&quot;639&quot; data-end=&quot;655&quot;&gt;Excepción 2:&lt;/span&gt; La descripción supera los 500 caracteres. El sistema informa el límite permitido y solicita ajustar el texto.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr style=&quot;height:25.75pt&quot;&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-width: 1.125pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Poscondiciones&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-width: 1.125pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;El producto cuenta con identidad técnica y descriptiva.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr style=&quot;height:25.75pt&quot;&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-width: 1.125pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Dependencias&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-width: 1.125pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&